# Basic Currency Converter

## Overview
This Python script converts amounts from one currency to another using real-time exchange rates fetched from an API.

## Setup
1. Clone the repository.
2. Install required packages: `pip install -r requirements.txt`.
3. Set your API key as an environment variable: `export EXCHANGE_API_KEY='your_api_key'`.

## Usage
Run the script with `python converter.py` and follow the on-screen prompts to perform currency conversions.

